original_title: 朝比奈ななせ AV DEBUT
overview: A 19-year-old beautiful girl with a big smile and innocence has landed on SOD! Even though I'm about to be crushed by tension and shame, I'm sure I'll die as I work hard one by one! I can't stand the occasional mature expression and the gap that writhes in pleasure! Keep an eye on Nanase-chan, who dyes all the viewers in a'Nana'color.
title: Asahina Nanase AV DEBUT
